1
00:00:58,800 --> 00:01:00,460
Here, sir, take a look at this.

2
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:14,480
The Right Wise King has always been treacherous.

3
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:15,539
This must be a trap.

4
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:19,280
This trip will be extremely dangerous.

5
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:22,240
Even if it's a living hell,

6
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:24,760
I have to give it a try.

7
00:01:44,759 --> 00:01:48,400
That person locked in the third tent,

8
00:01:48,759 --> 00:01:51,020
why does the prince take him everywhere?

9
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:52,890
Do you think he's there?

10
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:54,770
Let's go.

11
00:02:36,600 --> 00:02:37,280
Father!

12
00:02:40,480 --> 00:02:41,120
Father!

13
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,520
Qingshu?

14
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:56,600
My daughter?

15
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,600
No, it's impossible.

16
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:05,890
It's another dream.

17
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:07,840
A dream.

18
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:09,320
Father.

19
00:03:10,600 --> 00:03:11,660
This is not a dream.

20
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:13,520
I am your daughter.

21
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:15,240
I... I am Qingshu.

22
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,720
I'm sorry, Father.

23
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:20,240
I'm too late.

24
00:03:35,200 --> 00:03:35,880
Father.

25
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,880
Who did this to you?

26
00:03:41,320 --> 00:03:42,360
Three years ago,

27
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:45,220
Prince Ling hosted a banquet.

28
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:47,620
He pretended to discuss border affairs,

29
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,520
but it was actually a trap.

30
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:53,570
He forced me to hand over the officials' records.

31
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:57,170
I swore to death not to obey.

32
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:03,400
He actually stabbed me when I was not prepared.

33
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:09,040
I was seriously injured and near death,

34
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:12,900
and secretly handed over to the Right Virtuous Prince of Beidi by him.

35
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:18,320
I faintly heard him say,

36
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:20,700
"This person is still useful.

37
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,820
Keep a close watch on him."

38
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:30,440
The Official Conduct Records are royal secrets.

39
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:33,490
How could they fall into the hands of traitors

40
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:35,650
and fail Your Majesty's trust?

41
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,640
Father.

42
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:41,560
Qingshu.

43
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:44,159
The Right Worthy Prince said

44
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:48,680
Prince Ling forged evidence of my collusion with the enemy.

45
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:50,690
The Emperor was furious

46
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:54,920
and decreed the execution of our entire Yan family.

47
00:04:56,159 --> 00:04:57,560
Is this true?

48
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:58,480
Father,

49
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:01,730
the whole Yan family is safe and sound.

50
00:05:02,080 --> 00:05:03,960
Cui Tingru has been executed.

51
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:08,880
Good.

52
00:05:10,200 --> 00:05:11,360
He deserved it.

53
00:05:12,400 --> 00:05:13,880
That man deserved to die.

54
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,400
Uncle Yan,

55
00:05:17,520 --> 00:05:20,160
I am Xiao Jingyan, son of Xiao Muyu.

56
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:22,720
Jingyan.

57
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,320
Uncle Yan.

58
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:24,680
It's not safe to stay here.

59
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:25,600
I'll take you away first.

60
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:26,720
Okay. Let's go.

61
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:27,640
Go.

62
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:28,560
Father.

63
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:56,120
What a touching father-daughter reunion.

64
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,120
Prince Xiao.

65
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:00,280
Miss Yan.

66
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,040
I have been

67
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,760
waiting for you for a long time.

68
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:06,090
Right Virtuous Prince,

69
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:08,340
you're still as treacherous as ever.

70
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:11,760
My so-called methods

71
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:15,330
are exactly for dealing with people like you.

72
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:17,560
Miss Yan.

73
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:20,320
Do you really want to take your father

74
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,410
and leave this place right now?

75
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,560
It's simple.

76
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:27,800
Just hand over the Officials' Records,

77
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:29,900
and I will let him go immediately.

78
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:32,000
In your dreams!

79
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:37,360
It seems

80
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:41,400
you have all decided to die together today.

81
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:42,800
Take them!

82
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:43,880
Stop!

83
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:49,520
Let them go.

84
00:06:50,400 --> 00:06:52,130
I will tell you the whereabouts

85
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,320
of the Officials' Records.

86
00:06:54,320 --> 00:06:54,920
Father!

87
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:12,360
They really don't know

88
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:15,260
the whereabouts of the Officials' Records.

89
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:17,720
Go to hell, Di dogs!

90
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:20,120
Uncle Yan!

91
00:07:36,159 --> 00:07:37,480
I, Yan Mingtang,

92
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:40,170
have a clear conscience before heaven

93
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:41,880
and earth.

94
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:44,520
I have been loyal to the sovereign and country,

95
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:46,450
and have never committed treason.

96
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:49,440
I only failed my wife.

97
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:53,880
Chop this old thing into pieces

98
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:55,600
and drag him out to feed the dogs.

99
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:56,320
No!

100
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:00,000
Father!

101
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,280
Qingshu,

102
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:07,400
apologize to your mother for me.

103
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,440
Take her down as well.

104
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:12,680
No! No!

105
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:13,240
Stop!

106
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:14,840
No! Don't take me away.

107
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:16,240
Stop!

108
00:08:16,280 --> 00:08:18,080
Don't take my father's body away.

109
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:18,680
Stop!

110
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:19,320
Hold on.

111
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,640
No!

112
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:27,850
Prince Youxian.

113
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:32,559
Although I don't know the whereabouts of the officials' records,

114
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:33,360
today,

115
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:36,200
as long as you let us leave

116
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:38,480
and return Uncle Yan's body,

117
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,240
I am willing to

118
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:43,200
exchange the map of the Heishui Valley iron mine.

119
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:43,840
All right.

120
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:45,000
Lord Xiao,

121
00:08:45,760 --> 00:08:47,620
I respect your family's loyalty.

122
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,560
I'll do you a favor today.

123
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:52,250
You must keep your promise.

124
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,360
Hand over the map,

125
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,370
and return the body.

126
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:16,690
I have prepared the golden-thread nanmu coffin.

127
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:19,340
The duke's appearance

128
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:22,220
has also been properly arranged.

129
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:23,160
Rest assured.

130
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:45,100
This is the Black Dragon Pendant.

131
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:48,040
You already know its origin.

132
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:51,560
My mother once said,

133
00:10:53,400 --> 00:10:55,000
if I meet the love of my life,

134
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:57,240
I must personally

135
00:10:58,600 --> 00:11:00,600
tie the Black Dragon Pendant on her.

136
00:11:14,560 --> 00:11:16,290
You must take care of yourself.

137
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:18,970
Get some rest early.

138
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:54,410
If the source of the poison is unknown,

139
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:56,610
it may be difficult to cure.

140
00:12:48,480 --> 00:12:49,120
This is...

141
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,600
My lord!

142
00:12:54,160 --> 00:12:56,120
My lord,

143
00:12:57,200 --> 00:13:01,600
how could you leave us behind?

144
00:13:01,640 --> 00:13:02,400
Madam Zhou,

145
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:05,440
your wailing is even more entertaining

146
00:13:06,040 --> 00:13:08,880
than a brothel singer's.

147
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:11,880
I'm afraid if Father's spirit is watching,

148
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:14,760
your noise will give him no peace.

149
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:19,700
Sister is disrespecting our stepmother again.

150
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:21,000
How unruly.

151
00:13:21,480 --> 00:13:22,680
Sister, your makeup

152
00:13:22,800 --> 00:13:24,320
is exquisitely done.

153
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:26,800
Father has just passed away,

154
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:28,560
and you're in the mood to put on makeup.

155
00:13:28,560 --> 00:13:29,200
Qingshu!

156
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:30,840
How could you hit us?

157
00:13:31,040 --> 00:13:32,240
I am your stepmother,

158
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:33,840
and she is your stepsister.

159
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:35,920
You constantly bully us.

160
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,520
Do you have any manners at all?

161
00:13:37,520 --> 00:13:39,780
I, Yan Qingshu, only follow my own rules.

162
00:13:39,880 --> 00:13:41,960
I'll hit and scold whoever I want.

163
00:13:42,560 --> 00:13:43,560
What do your rules

164
00:13:43,760 --> 00:13:44,720
have to do with me?

165
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:45,560
Yan Qingshu.

166
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:47,160
Father is gone,

167
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:49,720
and the Yan family is now in our hands.

168
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:51,960
We won't let you run wild here.

169
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:53,520
You stole the nest,

170
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:55,020
and still dare to talk big.

171
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:56,080
Today,

172
00:13:56,560 --> 00:13:57,800
I will show you

173
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:59,920
what my rules are.

174
00:14:00,920 --> 00:14:01,780
Someone, come.

175
00:14:02,040 --> 00:14:04,880
Madame Zhou and her daughter are out of their minds from grief.

176
00:14:04,880 --> 00:14:06,560
Serve them the calming soup.

177
00:14:07,560 --> 00:14:08,360
Yan Qingshu,

178
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,480
what are you doing?

179
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:10,960
What are you doing?

180
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:13,060
What are you doing?

181
00:14:14,520 --> 00:14:15,920
Force the medicine down.

182
00:14:16,040 --> 00:14:17,280
Force it all down.

183
00:14:17,520 --> 00:14:18,560
Don't leave a single drop.

184
00:14:18,560 --> 00:14:19,400
Hurry up,

185
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:20,560
pour it in.

186
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:24,520
Mother!

187
00:14:27,920 --> 00:14:29,320
What are you trying to do?

188
00:14:41,280 --> 00:14:42,880
Do you understand the rules now?

189
00:14:42,880 --> 00:14:45,080
I do.

190
00:14:45,240 --> 00:14:46,080
You bitch!

191
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:48,850
It seems my sister still doesn't understand.

192
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:55,440
This Heart-breaking Powder

193
00:14:55,480 --> 00:14:57,280
will rot your skin upon contact.

194
00:14:57,680 --> 00:14:59,160
There is only one antidote.

195
00:14:59,160 --> 00:15:00,400
Whoever grabs it

196
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:01,320
gets it.

197
00:15:04,320 --> 00:15:05,240
Mingli!

198
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:06,880
Mingli!

199
00:15:08,600 --> 00:15:09,160
It hurts.

200
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:10,840
Ah, it hurts.

201
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:13,280
It hurts.

202
00:15:13,400 --> 00:15:14,280
Yan Qingshu,

203
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:16,410
hand over the antidote!

204
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:21,360
Give me my antidote.

205
00:15:24,480 --> 00:15:25,360
What antidote?

206
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:29,600
Did my sister only prepare poison,

207
00:15:29,880 --> 00:15:31,080
without an antidote?

208
00:15:31,360 --> 00:15:33,420
What nonsense are you talking about?

209
00:15:35,560 --> 00:15:36,800
Then just wait,

210
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:40,240
and watch your mother rot to death.

211
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:42,210
Yan Qingshu!

212
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:43,520
Mingli.

213
00:15:43,520 --> 00:15:44,520
Mother!

214
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:46,160
Mingli, it hurts.

215
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:48,640
I'm in so much pain.

216
00:15:54,520 --> 00:15:55,560
Yan Qingshu!

217
00:16:22,080 --> 00:16:23,040
Cuimei

218
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:26,680
Huachao

219
00:16:26,680 --> 00:16:27,540
Weikun Huachao

220
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:30,960
Longcong Biaohao

221
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:34,360
Bin

222
00:16:34,360 --> 00:16:34,960
Shuangbin

223
00:16:35,240 --> 00:16:35,840
Ningzheng

224
00:16:35,920 --> 00:16:36,520
Ningzheng

225
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:39,840
Haochun Kangshuaihua

226
00:16:43,240 --> 00:16:43,720
Weichao

227
00:16:45,640 --> 00:16:47,600
Qiangyuan Liangbo

228
00:17:02,120 --> 00:17:02,480
Xi

229
00:17:03,280 --> 00:17:03,410
Xi

230
00:17:04,040 --> 00:17:04,400
Xi

231
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:04,880
Taoqiang Xi

232
00:17:04,880 --> 00:17:05,800
Taoqiang

233
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:10,880
Huiyue Yunqing.

234
00:17:14,359 --> 00:17:14,880
Yiyi.

235
